hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Where do you live? aban pharmacy Lisa Pan, Vice President of Rekoo, said that London could act as an intermediary between the Chinese parent company and largely untapped European opportunities. "Opening up an office in London's Tech City is a great move for Rekoo as it allows us to be the bridge between the European and Chinese mobile gaming markets," Pan said. "Companies in the UK produce very high quality games, and being in London means we can attract world-class talent and find new business opportunities with UK and European developers."
